    <item>
      <title>Basic Syntax</title>
      <link>https://xtimesai.github.io/en/post/2020/jan/syntax/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://xtimesai.github.io/en/post/2020/jan/syntax/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Headings&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To create a heading, add number signs (#) in front of a word or phrase. The number of number signs you use should correspond to the heading level. For example, to create a heading level three (h3), use three number signs (e.g., ### My Header).&#xA; &lt;/p&gt;</description>
